{"tid":1725481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真 ‧ 前罪犯法官高浩文未審先判指示威者為「罪犯」","createTime":"2019-11-15T18:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T07:21:13.000Z","uid":305299,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7f380fbdfb757599ee6449509742d06a7516e7","tid":1725481,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20140828/photo/bkn-20140828140547393-0828_00822_001_01p.jpg?20140828144940\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140828%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20140828140547393-0828_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20140828144940&h=4d15f293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現任高等法院法官高浩文 (Russel Coleman) 今日 (15號) 處理政府申請禁制令禁止係連登煽動暴力嘅時候，依位法官喺未有正式審訊嫌犯下，卻下達判詞直呼示威者為「罪犯」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲話「自我審查」唔一定係壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識法律嘅小弟，印象中，人權法同普通法入面好似有樣野叫無罪推論原則，唔明點解喺依位法官判決個陣唔講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想請教各位<br />\n<br />\n但係，原來其實只要翻查網上資料，今日處理禁制令嘅法庭入面，的確有一名罪犯，就係法官自己本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根據 SCMP 喺1999年嘅報導，當時仲未係法官嘅佢，懷疑向大律師公會隱瞞自己嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">刑事犯罪記錄</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而需要面臨公會嘅調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上佢嘅相片唔多，比較清楚嘅就係上面東方日報依一張佢仲未係法官嘅相，希望大家透過依次機會多認識一下依位法官，話唔定好快有一日佢會成為香港終審庭嘅首席大法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但到時香港嘅法治都唔知會係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n向好嘅方面諗，大家可以同被捕嘅手足講，唔好太擔心，其實有犯罪記錄都唔代表世界未日，將來話唔定有機會可以做法官架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時代革命<br />\n===== 蘋果日報：官直指示威者是罪犯 延續煽暴臨禁令打擊幕後煽惑者 =====<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191115&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60271944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191115%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60271944&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=062920da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191115%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60271944&h=ddbcdd7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191115&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60271944</a><br />\n===== 東方日報：(相片) 港視覆核案續審 政府被指最初無就發牌設限 =====<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20140828/bkn-20140828140547393-0828_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140828%2Fbkn-20140828140547393-0828_00822_001.html&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=acf39508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20140828/bkn-20140828140547393-0828_00822_001.html</a><br />\n===== SCMP ：Convicted lawyer faces Bar inquiry =====<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/article/286231/convicted-lawyer-faces-bar-inquiry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Farticle%2F286231%2Fconvicted-lawyer-faces-bar-inquiry&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=1fc3e461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/article/286231/convicted-lawyer-faces-bar-inquiry</a>"},{"pid":"692b250bbdc3bf96b0f3343e4197494c925f9c9a","tid":1725481,"uid":208508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"依啲冇人推？"},{"pid":"651a5516fbd567bc11b56319593febbb7470b955","tid":1725481,"uid":22529,"like